sections.Biography:
===Background===
[[File:Maron_Greyjoy_deayth.png|thumb|left|Maron is crushed beneath a falling tower.]]
Maron was the second son of [[Balon Greyjoy]] and [[Alannys Greyjoy|Alannys Harlaw]]. Balon is the head of [[House Greyjoy]] and the [[Lord Reaper of Pyke]]. Maron has two brothers, [[Rodrik Greyjoy|Rodrik]] - the oldest - and [[Theon Greyjoy|Theon]] - the youngest -, and a sister, [[Yara Greyjoy|Yara]], born after Maron. Maron became his father's heir after Rodrik died in battle, and was himself by a collapsing tower during the [[Siege of Pyke]].&lt;ref name=&quot;viewers guide&quot;&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season2/#!/guide/appendix/greyjoy-rebellion/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 appendices, Greyjoy Rebellion entry]&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 1]]===
Tyrion wonders what Balon would make of Theon's loyalty to [[House Stark]] given that he is Balon's only surviving son.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
